 \binom{n}{k}\left(1-\frac \lambda n\right)^{n-k}\left(\frac \lambda n\right)^k 
n\to\infty
 \begin{align} &\lim_{n\to\infty}\binom{n}{k}\left(1-\frac \lambda n\right)^{n-k}\left(\frac \lambda n\right)^k\\ &=\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac nn\frac{n-1}n\frac{n-2}n\dots\frac{n-k+1}{n} \left(1-\frac \lambda n\right)^{n-k}\frac{\lambda^k}{k!}\\ &=e^{-\lambda}\frac{\lambda^k}{k!} \end{align} 
